<h2 class="text-label">How to vote for your favorite joke:</h2>
<p style="color: white;">Just select on the "Vote" option on the left, select your favourite and click the "Vote" button next to you favourite joke. Please note that you only get to vote once.</p>
<p style="color: white;">Don't vote right away, give it some time for more jokes to roll in and set a reminder to check out all the jokes the last day (November 30th). You can make you choice then. If you want to cancel or change your vote, please contact Carlo (see contact details further below).</p>
<br>
