<b class="text-label">The "fine print":</b>
<p style="color: white;">Please don't forget to donate! Any jokes that have been added without a donation received will be disqualified. Please contact Carlo for exceptions of if you encounter any issues.</p>
<p style="color: white;">The winner will be announced on December 1st, 2023. The winner will be contacted via email and will be asked to provide their preferred method of payment. The winner will have 30 days to claim their prize. If the prize is not claimed within 30 days, the full prize will be donated to Movember.</p>
